              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="image">
            <img src="/public/images/micHero.png" alt="Mic" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="layout" id="sec2">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="title">What is Vibrer?</div>

          <div class="grid">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="desc">
                Vibrer is your ultimate destination for a musical journey like
                no other. It's a dynamic platform that seamlessly blends the
                world of music and social interaction. With Vibrer, you can
                explore diverse genres, connect with talented artists, enjoy
                live performances, and even participate in contests. Elevate
                your passion for music and engage with a vibrant community of
                music enthusiasts. Discover, connect, and experience music on a
                whole new level with Vibrer.
                <span class="toFeatures" onclick="scrollToFeatures() "
                  >View features</span
                >
              </div>

              <div class="v-wrapper" id="videoPlay">
                <img src="./public/images/listening-to.jpg" alt="bg" />
                <img
                  class="play-btn"
                  src="./public/images/play-button.svg"
                  alt="play button"
                />
                <div class="title">Watch Vibrer's short promo</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="img-wrapper">
                <img
                  src="./public/images/skeleton-music.jpg"
                  alt="Vibrer's realm"
                />
                <div class="title">
                  Melodies <br />
                  Beyond Time: <br />
                  Vibrer's Realm
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="sect3">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="left">
              <div class="title">Who is Vibrer for?</div>
              <div class="subtitle">
                Built Exclusively for Music Industry Artists
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Vibrer is a platform crafted for music enthusiasts and creators
                alike. Whether you're an aspiring singer, a talented musician,
                or a passionate dancer, Vibrer provides a space to showcase your
                artistry, connect with fans, and unlock opportunities. Our
                vibrant community offers a hub for discovering new talents,
                enjoying live performances, and engaging with your favorite
                artists. Whether you're seeking inspiration or aiming to amplify
                your musical journey, Vibrer empowers you to express and
                experience the magic of music like never before.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
              <div class="imgWrapper">
                <div class="title">Singers</div>
                <img src="/public/images/singer.png" alt="Singer" />
              </div>
              <div class="imgWrapper">
                <div class="title">Musicains</div>
                <img src="/public/images/musician.png" alt="Musician" />
              </div>
              <div class="imgWrapper">
                <div class="title">Dancers</div>
                <img src="/public/images/dancer.png" alt="Dancer" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="sec4">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="grid2">
            <div class="title">
              Explore Vibrer's <br />
              Unique Features
            </div>
            <div class="mtitle">Explore Vibrer's Unique Features</div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/music_pink.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div class="sTitle">
                Elevate your music experience with Vibrer's cutting-edge tools.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="grid3">
            <div class="title">Dynamic social media inspired profile</div>
            <div class="desc">
              Craft a dynamic social media-inspired profile that not only
              showcases your artistic essence but also connects you with fans.
              This feature empowers you to thrive in the music community,
              creating an immersive experience that goes beyond mere
              functionality.
            </div>
            <img src="/public/images/Gravity-Scene.png" alt="Gravity" />
          </div>

          <div class="grid5">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/send_pink.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Share Your Passion</div>

                <div class="desc">
                  Amplify your presence by effortlessly sharing your music,
                  videos, and creations with a global audience. Connect,
                  inspire, and grow through vibrant content sharing on Vibrer.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/fast-forward.svg" alt="icon" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Browse and Connect</div>
                <div class="desc">
                  Explore a world of diverse musical talents and connect with
                  like-minded enthusiasts. Discover new genres, follow your
                  favorite artists, and build a vibrant community on Vibrer.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/message-text-01.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Seamless Communication</div>

                <div class="desc">
                  Engage in lively discussions, express your thoughts, and
                  connect with artists and fans using Vibrer's intuitive inbuilt
                  chat system.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/live_concert.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Exclusive Live Concerts</div>
                <div class="desc">
                  Immerse yourself in extraordinary live performances by
                  celebrated artists, available exclusively on Vibrer.
                  Experience the energy of live music from the convenience of
                  your device.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/contest.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Online Contests</div>
                <div class="desc">
                  Participate in online contests on Vibrer. Step up to the
                  challenge by participating in singing contests, dance-offs,
                  and more, Showcase your artistry, secure votes, and win prizes
                  on Vibrer.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">
                <img src="/public/images/icons/live_stream.svg" alt="" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="title">Live Streaming</div>

                <div class="desc">
                  Feel the beat in real-time with Vibrer's Live Streaming.
                  Artists go live, fans connect, and virtual gifts flow, all at
                  your fingertips.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="gnform">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="title">Subscribe to our news letter!</div>
          <div class="subtitle">
            Stay informed about Vibrer's upcoming launch by providing your
            details. Join us on this musical adventure!
          </div>

          <form id="mailingList">
            <div class="grid">
              <input
                type="hidden"
                name="mailType"
                value="Launch notifications"
              />
              <div class="col">
                <input
                  class="form-input"
                  type="text"
                  placeholder="First Name"
                  name="firstName"
                />
                <div class="form-alert"></div>
              </div>

              <div class="col">
                <input
                  class="form-input"
                  type="text"
                  placeholder="Last Name"
                  name="lastName"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="col">
                <input
                  class="form-input"
                  type="email"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="Email"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="col">
                <button class="btn btn-primary ml-btn">Subscribe</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              By submitting this form, you agree to receive updates and
              notifications from Vibrer. We respect your privacy and won't share
              your information with third parties.
              <a href="./privacy">Read our privacy policy</a>
            </div>

            <button
              type="button"
              class="btn btn-outlined"
              onclick="scrollToMoreFeatures()"
            >
              Continue Exploring Features
              <img
                class="img-right"
                src="./public/images/arrow-down-circle.svg"
                alt="circle arrow"
              />
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="layout" id="sec5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="grid2">
            <div class="col">
              <img
                class="social-hub"
                src="./public/images/edited-for-vib.png"
                alt="social hub image"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Vibrer's Social Hub</div>
              <div class="desc">
                Elevate your experience with Vibrer's integrated Social Hub
                feature. Enhance your presence and empower creators to flourish
                within a vibrant artistic community.
              </div>
              <div class="desc icon">
                <img src="./public/images/check-circle.svg" alt="Check" />
                <div>
                  Fans engage with music, videos, live streams, concerts,
                  contests through likes, comments, playlist, bookmarks etc.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="desc icon">
                <img src="./public/images/check-circle.svg" alt="Check" />
                <div>
                  Artists can captivate their audience with Music, images,
                  videos, polls and earn a passive income
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Join Vibrer's interconnected community, where music enthusiasts
                and creators unite to celebrate their passion and connect like
                never before.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="layout" id="sec6">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="title">Earn and manage funds through inbuilt wallet</div>
          <div class="desc">
            "Earn a passive income on Vibrer by sharing music videos and audio
            files, participating in contests, performing live concerts, offering
            one-to-one performances, and live streaming. Monetize your content
            and build a stronger relationship with your audience.
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          class="walletimg"
          src="./public/images/wallet.png"
          alt="Wallet image"
        />
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer'); %>
    <div id="overlay">
      <!-- The popup content -->
      <div id="popup">
        <iframe id="video" src="" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="success-pop">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="success-pop-title">Thank you!</div>
        <div class="success-pop-close">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="success-pop-desc">
        You have been added to our mailing list.
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- javascript -->
    <script src="/public/js/cookieBanner.js?v=2.0"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/theme-v01node.js?v=2.0"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/forms.js?v=2.0"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/languageSwitcher.js"></script>

    <script>
      const allElements = document.querySelectorAll("body *");

      allElements.forEach((el) => {
        if (el.offsetWidth > document.documentElement.clientWidth) {
          console.log("Overflowing element:", el);
        }
      });
    </script>
    <script>
      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        // Your YouTube video ID
        // var videoID = "WFlYEXkcLJ8";

        // The clickable div
        var clickableDiv = document.getElementById("videoPlay");

        // The overlay
        var overlay = document.getElementById("overlay");

        // The video iframe
        var video = document.getElementById("video");

        clickableDiv.addEventListener("click", function () {
          // Show the overlay
          overlay.style.display = "block";

          // Set the source for the iframe and autoplay
          video.src = "https://static.vibrer.app/mediavid/vibrer-promo-v1.mp4";

          ("?autoplay=1");
        });

        // Hide overlay when clicked
        overlay.addEventListener("click", function () {
          overlay.style.display = "none";
          // Stop the video
          video.src = "";
        });
      });
    </script>
    <script>
      function scrollToGNForm() {
        const gnForm = document.getElementById("gnform");
        if (gnForm) {
          window.scrollTo({
            top: gnForm.offsetTop,
            behavior: "smooth",
          });
        }
      }

      function scrollToFeatures() {
        const sec4 = document.getElementById("sec4");
        if (sec4) {
          window.scrollTo({
            top: sec4.offsetTop,
            behavior: "smooth",
          });
        }
      }
      function scrollToMoreFeatures() {
        const sec5 = document.getElementById("sec5");
        if (sec5) {
          window.scrollTo({
            top: sec5.offsetTop,
            behavior: "smooth",
          });
        }
      }
      function learnMore() {
        const sec2 = document.getElementById("sec2");
        if (sec2) {
          window.scrollTo({
            top: sec2.offsetTop,
            behavior: "smooth",
          });
        }
      }
    </script>
    <script>
      function toContest() {
        window.location.href = "/contest";
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
